{"tid":2233860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"SpaceX奪得美軍近12億軍用衛星合同","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:46:13.000Z","uid":295230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"741f54c29eb6caabdb6e0dc9051c0856200a2ccb","tid":2233860,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:36:27.000Z","msg":"SpaceX 與美國軍方之間的關係持續在增溫中，繼 GPS 等衛星的發射合約後，現在連打造衛星的合約都到手了。據 Space News 報導，美國太空發展署與 SpaceX 及 L3 Harris 兩間公司簽訂了分別價值 1.49 億美元與 1.93 億美元的合約，打造一共用於識別和監控新一代超高速導彈的八枚飛彈預警衛星。<br />\n<br />\n太空發展署署長 Derek Tournear 向 Space News 表示，SpaceX 的衛星將以 Starlink 同樣的機身為基礎，但裝上了廣角的紅外線攝影機，可以持續監控是否有飛彈發射時所產生的火光。依合約要求，八枚衛星需在 2022 年九月前升空，與洛馬等其他公司所打造的通訊、目標追蹤衛星組成衛星群，且太空發展署還保留擴大衛星群的可能，最後預警衛星的數量可能會超過 28 枚之譜。<br />\n<br />\n前2日放既材確認左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f61451c08846735681e572edcdc23a36a4fa61f","tid":2233860,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"前2日放既料確認左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958bcc85a9fad54ff26d259f861a5c23effc5327","tid":2233860,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"SpaceX幾時IPO <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0478864d49047a4ecc2533c5315cad3ccb896d","tid":2233860,"uid":116087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"冇上市呢可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9a88bbd207d4aa07a616fe3da47d6c8b577bc4","tid":2233860,"uid":110988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"幾時會一股tesla送一股spaceX<img src=\"/assets/faces/